## 🚀 Installation

1. Download or clone this repo:
   ```bash
   git clone https://github.com/HITBZack/booqwp.git
Place the folder into your WordPress /wp-content/plugins/ directory

Activate the plugin in your WordPress dashboard

Done! The default Booqable modal will be fully replaced 🎉

🧪 Customization (UI customization wizard will be added)
Edit css/bwp-style.css to change modal layout or colors

Modify templates/modal-template.php for different markup

Extend js/bwp-itempopup.js to handle additional interactions

Need to match your own brand colors? Update the styles using your palette (e.g. #9f8170, #b9c8ad, cream tones, etc.).

